title: #92Noon! Warren/Cy/Fran/TJackMemories
description: Big 10 Commish Kevin Warren starts off the show! A young man named Quincy Morgan raised $3600 for Adam Thielen's Covid Relief radiothon and joins, Cy Amundson from the bunker, Fran Tarkenton with HOF-level stories, and some thoughts on the passing of Tarvaris Jackson. Football/draft nuggets sprinkled in as well!
